description:
Brooke and Danielle are out east for the summer and chatting about their past few weeks of life.  Danielle shares stories from her time at her family reunion in Illinois, and Brooke discusses her visit to Atlantic City.  Brooke and Danielle talk about swimming lessons, trivia games and all of the VARIOUS eras the gals are in.  The gals have an interesting few weeks coming up, so stay tuned for all of the fun.  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies and stories!
